@page "/services"

<PageTitle>Our Services - YasirSteel</PageTitle>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="hero" style="min-height: 40vh; padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Our Services</h1>
            <p>Comprehensive steel manufacturing solutions tailored to meet diverse construction and industrial requirements.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Services -->
<section class="page-section section-white">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Core Manufacturing Services</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🔧</div>
                <h3>Cut & Bend Services</h3>
                <p><strong>Precision Engineering for Your Projects</strong></p>
                <p>Our advanced cutting and bending services provide reinforcement steel bars manufactured according to Saudi (SSA), American (ASTM, ACI), British (BS), and other international standards. We offer:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #666;">
                    <li>Precision cutting to exact specifications</li>
                    <li>Complex bending configurations</li>
                    <li>Custom shapes and dimensions</li>
                    <li>CAD-based cutting schedules</li>
                    <li>Quality assurance testing</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🕸️</div>
                <h3>Welded Wire Mesh</h3>
                <p><strong>Superior Strength and Durability</strong></p>
                <p>High-quality welded wire mesh manufactured to meet BS 4483, DIN 488, ASTM A185, and A497 standards. Our welded wire mesh products feature:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #666;">
                    <li>Consistent weld quality</li>
                    <li>Various mesh sizes and configurations</li>
                    <li>Rigorous quality control testing</li>
                    <li>Test certificates issued on request</li>
                    <li>Custom panel sizes available</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">⚙️</div>
                <h3>Cold Rolled Wire Products</h3>
                <p><strong>Premium Wire Solutions</strong></p>
                <p>Specialized supply of premium Cold Rolled Wire Products designed for extensive applications across various industries. Our offerings include:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #666;">
                    <li>High tensile strength wire</li>
                    <li>Consistent diameter tolerance</li>
                    <li>Superior surface finish</li>
                    <li>Various diameter options</li>
                    <li>Bulk supply capabilities</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">📏</div>
                <h3>Wire Straightening & Cutting</h3>
                <p><strong>Precision Processing Services</strong></p>
                <p>Advanced wire straightening and cutting services using state-of-the-art machinery to ensure precise dimensions and superior finish:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #666;">
                    <li>Automated straightening process</li>
                    <li>Precise length cutting</li>
                    <li>Minimal waste generation</li>
                    <li>Fast turnaround times</li>
                    <li>Quality inspection throughout</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Additional Services -->
<section class="page-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Additional Services</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🏗️</div>
                <h3>Construction Solutions</h3>
                <p>Comprehensive reinforcement solutions for construction projects of all sizes, from residential buildings to large infrastructure developments. We provide technical consultation and project-specific solutions.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🚚</div>
                <h3>Logistics & Delivery</h3>
                <p>Efficient logistics network ensuring timely delivery of products across Pakistan. Our large stockyard capacity allows us to maintain ready inventory for immediate dispatch to project sites.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">📋</div>
                <h3>Technical Consultation</h3>
                <p>Expert technical consultation services to help architects, engineers, and contractors choose the right steel solutions for their specific project requirements and structural needs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">📜</div>
                <h3>Quality Certification</h3>
                <p>Comprehensive test certificates and quality documentation for all products. We provide detailed material certificates, test reports, and compliance documentation as required.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Standards & Specifications -->
<section class="page-section section-white">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Standards & Specifications</h2>
        <div class="quality-content">
            <div>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #1e3c72;">International Standards Compliance</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    YasirSteel products are manufactured in strict accordance with internationally recognized standards, ensuring global compatibility and reliability for all construction applications.
                </p>

                <div class="quality-features">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🇸🇦</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Saudi Standards (SSA)</strong><br>
                            Compliance with Saudi Standards Authority requirements for regional projects
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🇺🇸</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>American Standards (ASTM, ACI)</strong><br>
                            Meeting ASTM International and American Concrete Institute specifications
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🇬🇧</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>British Standards (BS)</strong><br>
                            Adherence to British Standards Institution quality requirements
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🇩🇪</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>German Standards (DIN)</strong><br>
                            Compliance with Deutsches Institut für Normung specifications
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #1e3c72;">Service Capabilities</h3>

                <div class="about-stats" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">150,000+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Tons Annual Production</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">30,000m²</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Facility Area</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Production Capability</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Projects Completed</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-top: 2rem;">
                    Our comprehensive service portfolio is backed by advanced manufacturing capabilities, extensive quality control measures, and a commitment to delivering exceptional results for every project.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Call to Action -->
<section class="page-section section-blue">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p style="color: white; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
            Contact our expert team today to discuss your steel requirements and receive a customized quote for your project.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Request Quote</a>
    </div>
</section>

